summary.span: 包含編譯器所產生但不適合在程式碼中直接使用的型別。

span.span: Contains compiler-generated types that are not intended to be used directly from your code.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 請勿使用，或包含此命名空間。Do not use or include this namespace. 此命名空間的目的是為容器類別是 XAML 標記編譯器產生的 XAML 類型解析對組件的內部協助程式。The purpose of this namespace is a container for the class is an internal helper that the XAML markup compiler produces for XAML type resolution against assemblies.
